c: 57
v: 13
t: "√Ďalnde naafiqii…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e naafiqii…ďe rew…ďe …ďen wi'anoyta gom…óim…ďe …ďen: \"Habbee men, men jalbinora annoora mon on\". ∆Āe wi'anee : \"Yiltoree …ďaawo mon, …óa…ď…ďoyon annoora\". Heedo wa…óee hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ngo damal ngal yurmeende woni e nder mun, …ďaawo maggal noon, ko lepte woni e bannge mun"